NAME

DateTime::Locale::chr_US - Locale data examples for the Cherokee United States (chr-US) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Cherokee United States locale.

Datetime Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ᏔᎵᏁᎢᎦ, ᎧᎦᎵ 5, 2008 ᎤᎾᎢ 6:30:30 ᏒᎯᏱᎢ UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = ᏧᎾᎩᎶᏍᏗ, ᎥᏍᎩᏱ 22, 1995 ᎤᎾᎢ 9:05:02 ᏌᎾᎴ UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = ᎤᎾᏙᏓᏈᏕᎾ, ᏚᎵᏍᏗ 15, -10 ᎤᎾᎢ 4:44:23 ᏌᎾᎴ UTC

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = ᎧᎦ 5, 2008, 6:30:30 ᏒᎯᏱᎢ
